test.query: SELECT SearchPhrase FROM hits_100m_single PREWHERE SearchPhrase != '' FORMAT Null
SELECT SearchPhrase FROM hits_100m_single WHERE SearchPhrase != '' ORDER BY EventTime LIMIT 10 FORMAT Null
SELECT SearchPhrase, MIN(URL), COUNT(*) AS c FROM hits_100m_single WHERE URL LIKE '%google%' AND SearchPhrase != '' GROUP BY SearchPhrase ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10 FORMAT Null
